Wɔ̃ɔn suru nɔɔbɑ yirusen sɔ̃ɔ yɛndɑ itɑse sɔɔrɑ Sɑlomɔɔ u derɑ tɔmbɑ wurɑ ben yɛnusɔ. Mɑ bɑ nuku dobu mɔ̀ durom mɛ Gusunɔ u Dɑfidi kɑ Sɑlomɔɔ kɑ sere win tɔmbu Isirelibɑ kuɑn sɔ̃.
