N deemɑ Yeroboɑmu, Nɛbɑtin bii, u rɑɑ kpikiru suɑ Sɑlomɔɔn sɔ̃ u dɑ u wɑ̃ɑ Egibitiɔ. Sɑnɑm mɛ u nuɑ Roboɑmu u bɑndu di, yerɑ u gɔsirɑmɑ Egibiti min di.
Roboɑmu u dɑ u sinɑ Yerusɑlɛmuɔ. Mɑ u Yudɑn wusu gbɑ̃rɑnu bɑnisi.
Roboɑmu u mɔwɑ wɔ̃ɔ weeru kɑ tiɑ sɑnɑm mɛ u bɑndu di Yerusɑlɛmuɔ. Mɑ u win bɑndun dɑm sire. U kuɑwɑ wɔ̃ɔ wɔkurɑ nɔɔbu kɑ yiru bɑndu sɔɔ Yerusɑlɛmu mi. N deemɑ wuu gerɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u gɔsɑ Isirelibɑ kpuron sɔ̃ gɑ n kɑ win yĩsiru sɔɔwɑ. Roboɑmu win mɛron yĩsirɑ Nɑɑmɑ, wi u sɑ̃ɑ Amɔni.
U Yudɑbɑ sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, bu Gusunɔ ben bɑɑbɑbɑn Yinni kɑsuo, kpɑ bu win yiirebu kɑ win woodɑbɑ mɛm nɔɔwɑ.
Mɑ tɑbu yɔ̃rɑ sɑɑ ye sɔɔ, sere n kɑ kuɑ Asɑn bɑndun wɔ̃ɔ tɛnɑ kɑ nɔɔbuse sɔɔ.
Bɛnyɑmɛɛn bweseru sɔɔ, Eliɑdɑ tɑbu kowo wɔrugɔwɑ u tɑbu kowobu nɔrɔbun subɑ goobu (200.000) kpɑre be bɑ tɛnnu kɑ tɛrɛnu mɔ.
Yerɑ hunde gɑɑ yɑ yɑrimɑ yɑ yɔ̃rɑ Yinni Gusunɔn wuswɑɑɔ yɑ nɛɛ, kon Akɑbu wi nɔni wɔ̃ke. Mɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u ye bikiɑ u nɛɛ, ɑmɔnɑ kɑɑ koosinɑ.
Mɑ u nɛɛ, Gusunɔ bɛsɛn bɑɑbɑbɑn Yinni, wunɑ ɑ sɑ̃ɑ Yinni wɔllɔ. Wunɑ ɑ bwesenu kpuron bɑndu nɛni. Wunɑ ɑ mɑɑ dɑm kpuro nɛni wunɛn nɔmɑɔ. Goo sɑri wi u koo kɑ nun tɑbu ko.
Yen biruwɑ goo nimkuu si, su kɔsikirɑ. Su ǹ mɑɑ kpĩɑ su Tɑɑsisi de.
Akɑsiɑn bwese te sɔɔ, goo sɑri wi u sɑ̃ɑ dee dee u kɑ bɑndu di.
Adɑmɑ Lefibɑ bɑ ǹ ye kue.
Mɑ Amɑsiɑ u sɔmɔ wi sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, ɑmɔnɑ kon ko tɛ̃ n kɑ nɛn sii geesun gobi tɔnnu itɑ ye mwɑ ye nɑ Isirelibɑn tɑbu kowo be wɛ̃ mi.
U mɑɑ kɔ̃su yenu bɑnɑ gbɑburɔ, mɑ u dɔkɔ dɑbi dɑbinu gbɑ, domi u sɑbe dɑbi dɑbinu mɔ ni nu wɑ̃ɑ Sefɑlɑn wɔwɑɔ kɑ nim wɔ̃kun goorɔ. Mɛyɑ u mɑɑ gbɑɑ wukobu mɔ kɑ be bɑ rɑ resɛm sɔmburu ko guunɔ kɑ guu te bɑ mɔ̀ Kɑɑmɛliɔ. Domi u rɑ gbee sɔmburu kɑ̃.
N deemɑ Yinni Gusunɔn sɔmɔ goo u wɑ̃ɑ mi. Win yĩsirɑ Odɛdi. Yerɑ u tɑbu kowo be sennɔ dɑ. U nɛɛ, wee Gusunɔ bɛɛn bɑɑbɑbɑn Yinni u kɑ Yudɑbɑ mɔru kuɑ, mɑ u bɛɛ bu nɔmu bɛriɑ, mɑ i bu go kɑ wɔnwɔndu sɑriru sere ben wuri yi nùn girɑri.
